dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jeffrey Rivera. May I please have your name?
Hello, my name is Melissa Barnes.
Nice to meet you, Melissa. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Yes, my policy number is three two four five.
Thank you, Melissa. Can you also confirm your date of birth for security purposes?
My date of birth is the fifth of December, one nine eight zero.
Great, thank you for confirming. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today, Melissa?
I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Melissa. I can assist you with that. Thank you for providing the necessary information.
Thank you for your time, Melissa. Have a wonderful day.
